  "instructions": [
    "Combine rice and water in a medium saucepan",
    "Bring to a boil and reduce heat to a simmer",
    "Cover and cook for 15 minutes or until liquid is absorbed",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together mustard and vegan yogurt",
    "Add thyme, salt, and pepper to the bowl and whisk until smooth",
    "Add sunflower oil to the bowl and whisk until emulsified",
    "Stir the emulsified mixture into the cooked rice",
    "Cook for an additional 2 minutes",
    "Serve hot"
